AXIS-Y x Beauty & Seoul 

Thank you for joining our live wirh @beauty_and_seoul 

Maree @mareekinder flew all the way from 🇬🇧 U.K. 

We had so much fun and cant wait to do more. 

Thank you for joining live everyone.

We were inspired by the Korean government's #StayStrongCampaign to support the fight against COVID-19 in communities worldwide. 🌐 Through our Mugwort Pore Clarifying Wash Off Pack, we wanted to add a relaxing, meditative, self-care moment for those that are spending more time at home during the pandemic. We also noticed members of our communities suffering from skin problems caused by everyday mask wear, dubbed by social media as “maskne”. We formulated our wash off pack with ingredients to help treat these stressful and painful skin irritations. 🌿

With a base of 61% Mugwort extract, our wash off pack clears the pores of impurities, soothes inflamed and irritated skin, and gently exfoliates dead skin to reveal a bright and healthy complexion. 💚
